'''Obah gas''' was a nerve gas that affected anything smaller than a [[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshan]] or a [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]]. The effects of obah gas could be reduced or negated by drinking the [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage, [[Reactor Core (drink)|Reactor Core]].

